Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat: Add Claude 3.7 & 3.5 pricing and 'show' command

- Added official pricing for Claude 3.7 Sonnet, 3.5 Sonnet, 3.5 Haiku, 3 Opus, 3 Sonnet, and 3 Haiku.
- Fixed 'findMostRecentJsonl' to strictly match 'messages.jsonl' to avoid parsing non-message JSONLs.
- Added '-c', '--cost', and 'show' arguments to view the cost of the last session without launching Claude Code.
- Updated README with the new models and instructions.
